{{expand Russian|date=February 2017}}
'''''Rejection''''' is a Ukrainian apocalyptic film directed by [[Vladimir Lert]] ([[:ru:Лерт, Владимир Владимирович|ru]]) with Sergei Babkin ([[:ru:Бабкин, Сергей Николаевич|ru]]) and [[Aleksandr Bashirov]]. It was made in 2009, but not released until 2011 in Ukrainian.<ref>http://www.phenixweb.info/Special-BIFFF-2011-Rejection-de-Vladimir-Lert</ref><ref>http://www.cinemafantastique.net/Rejection.html</ref> It was shown in Russian (as Отторжение) at the Ranok film festival in April 2012, and in Russian with English subtitles released on [[Amazon Prime]].
